#*'''2000,''' ''CSI'' (TV, episode 1.06)
#*:"Eddie said that she was into it." "'''He said, she said.''' It's about the evidence, Catherine."
#*'''2001,''' ''Frasier'' (TV, episode 8.23)
#*:'''He said, she said.''' We'll never know what really happened.